name: Mai Shuranai (SNK Fighter)
description:
Does she really need an introduction? It's Mai Shuranai. She wields a folding fan and fan service. Seems to work well with all models, but leans towards anime/drawn. Can be NSFW due to wardrobe malfunctions.

'maishu' is the trigger.

modelVersions.name: v1.0
modelVersions.description: 30+ images (drawings, cosplay, renders, etc) trained on SD1.5. Think it hits a good mix between giving you the flavor of the character without being stubborn.
